<a id="comment-5900"></a>
  <div class="comment">
    <h3 class="title"><a href="/green-u-s-transit-whopping-myth#comment-5900" class="active">Greener to ride?</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by Paul (not verified) on Mon, 2008-08-04 20:36.</div>
